Bolt Builds partnered with Telo Labs to design and build a revolutionary medical spa in New York City that merges science with hospitality. Conceived as a modern wellness destination, Telo Labs redefines the medical spa experience by creating an environment that feels both restorative, modern and elevated.

The design is anchored in contrast with rich, dark oak cabinetry and trim set against soft serene walls that establish a sense of warmth and sophistication. A custom reception desk, crafted from glass block panels with integrated lighting, serves as a luminous focal point that welcomes guests and sets the tone for the experience. Stainless steel details and curated material pairings further enhance the balance of modernity and elegance throughout the space.

Every corner of the spa was designed with intention, offering clients a refined environment that prioritizes comfort, care, and atmosphere. The interplay of textures through wood, glass, and steel creates a sleek yet inviting interior that reflects Telo Labs’ forward-thinking approach to wellness.

